.\" singine-collibra-server(1) — id-gen HTTP API server
.TH SINGINE\-COLLIBRA\-SERVER 1 "2026-03-25" "singine" "Singine Manual"
.
.SH NAME
singine\-collibra\-server \- id-gen HTTP API server (net/dmz modes)
.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B singine collibra server
.I command
.RI [ options ]
.
.SH DESCRIPTION
Starts and manages the id-gen HTTP API server defined in
.IR id-gen/server/server.sh .
Two access modes are supported:
.TP
.B net
Full API access. All endpoints available.
.TP
.B dmz
Restricted access. Only the four safe-to-expose endpoints are active:
.BR /health ,
.BR /api/id/gen ,
.BR /api/contracts/list ,
.BR /api/progress .
.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B singine collibra server start [\-\-port PORT] [\-\-mode net|dmz]
Start the server.
Default port:
.BR 7331 .
Default mode:
.BR net .
.TP
.B singine collibra server dmz [\-\-port PORT]
Shorthand for
.BR "start \-\-mode dmz" .
.TP
.B singine collibra server stop
Stop the running server.
.TP
.B singine collibra server status
Health check.
.
.SH ENDPOINTS
.TS
l l l.
Endpoint	net	dmz
GET /health	✓	✓
GET /api/id/gen	✓	✓
GET /api/contracts/list	✓	✓
GET /api/progress	✓	✓
(all other endpoints)	✓	✗
.TE
.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I id-gen/server/server.sh
Startup wrapper (auto-detects Lisp runtime: SBCL / CLISP / ECL / Guile).
.TP
.I id-gen/server/start.lisp
Common Lisp HTTP API implementation.
.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR singine\-collibra (1)
